title: Salmonella Dub - Feel The Seasons Change - live in concert with
description:
Salmonella Dub - Feel The Seasons Change - Live With The NZSO (vbr224kbs)

Feel the Seasons Change documents a unique collaboration between Salmonella Dub and the New Zealand Symphony Orchestra featuring guests Whirimako Black, Richard Nunns and Paddy Free.

Recorded live during the band's 2008 Feel The Seasons Change tour, it's a musical Journey through Aotearoa landscapes. Classic Salmonella Dub tracks are re invented by the incredible arrangements of NZSO arranger Tom Rainey.

Feel The Seasons Change will introduce the music of Salmonella Dub to a whole new audience, as well as being a brilliant memento of an incredible night of music.
